      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHEER DOWN (5) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 24.23 beating Reality Away. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Looks to have an edge on most of these. JUST ANGELIC (2) turned in a solid run last start over 425m at this track finishing 4th and beaten only one length (24.62). The form out of her last race has been franked. Has ability and can measure up. PAW LARA (1) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 1.5 lengths into third (22.58) at Ballarat in a Grade 5 over 390m. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Winning chance. RANGER'S GIRL (8) can fill a top-three spot.",
